838
01:30:10,920 --> 01:30:12,020
[SPEAKER_01] Da, naravno to.

839
01:30:12,020 --> 01:30:16,140
[SPEAKER_00] Problem, nazovimo to to problem, to je nešto puno krvavije.

840
01:30:16,140 --> 01:30:18,779
